Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.95,0:00:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the fake blueprints\Nthat you passed off on us earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.95,0:00:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I look at it carefully,\Nthere're signatures by the architects.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Tom," "Iceberg," and "Cutty Flam."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.84,0:00:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the end, there's a\Ncompany name: "Tom's Workers."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.97,0:00:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember hearing this\Nname Cutty Flam before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.39,0:00:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom's other disciple Cutty Flam is still alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.35,0:00:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and lives in this town...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...after changing his name to Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.66,0:01:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, you go ahead! Ahead of us!\NCut down the door and make a dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.79,0:01:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Go ahead!\N--What the hell?! Don't order me around!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.05,0:01:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Robin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Luffy!\N--Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.35,0:01:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin! I've finally found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.77,0:01:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy! Where the hell have you been?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin! I'm glad that I could see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.73,0:01:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a sec... What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.41,0:01:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.08,0:01:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Iceberg-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.79,0:01:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.13,0:01:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.97,0:02:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paulie... Why... didn't you run?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.98,0:02:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This looks... as if...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.61,0:02:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...they're the culprits who tried to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.67,0:02:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you guys dressed like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Kalifa...! Blueno...! Kaku...! Lucci...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.84,0:02:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop joking, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.81,0:02:51.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:55.65,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.65,0:02:58.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As power passes through our clasped hands
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:02.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.96,0:03:17.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Working together, let's ride the giant waves
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:24.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry toward the excitement--\Nthere's the starting signal
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:31.94,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to set sail-- let's raise anchor
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:39.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut through the rainbow-colored wind\Nand head for a sea of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:42.45,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a journey fraught with injury
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:46.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but what you cherish most will be right there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:50.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you get into a jam
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:53.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be there to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:57.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:04:01.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:04.18,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If a storm hits, let's put\Nour arms around each other
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:08.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and gaze at the light beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.47,0:04:12.39,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If we gather up the pieces of our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.39,0:04:15.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll make a map leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.69,0:04:18.65,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:24.45,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,under the same flag-- together, we're one
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:27.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,One Piece
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:43.05,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"Come Back, Robin! Showdown with CP9!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're some of the shipwrights\Nwho were with you! Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I know\Nthat square long-nosed guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could this mean... that the\Nassassination was an inside job?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:05:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paulie, to tell you the truth,\Nwe're Government intelligence agents.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you'd forgive us if we apologized, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.33,0:05:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were fellow shipwrights who worked\Ntogether building ships every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't believe me because this is too sudden,\Nshall I step on Iceberg's face or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop messing around! That's enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, the bull-masked man's voice I\Nheard earlier is the same voice as yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, you bastard! You can talk just fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.15,0:05:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you mock us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.49,0:05:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't, Paulie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pipe Hitch Knives!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finger Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still haven't learned your lesson, Paulie?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Rope guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this pointless resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've mastered techniques beyond\Nthe limits of human abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:06:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After years of training, these techniques,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,called the "Six Powers," allow human\Nbodies to be a match for weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once one masters them, he alone\Nis as strong as 100 people together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.94,0:07:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coo coo! Don't get carried away with gambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dummy! I was lucky today.\NThat's why I'm treating you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blueno! Bring us more alcohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.46,0:07:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kalifa! You're dressed like that again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.09,0:07:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Paulie. Just don't look at her. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you guys...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.11,0:07:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.78,0:07:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, you're gonna be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is sad, but my friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucci! You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.01,0:08:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Iron Body.\N--...Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? It's not working at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How annoying... Shave!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.89,0:08:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finger Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you had a flesh-and-blood body, you would've\Ngotten a hole in your neck and died instantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...rubber man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing, Straw Hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.98,0:09:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're planning to kill him, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.78,0:09:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were all shipwright\Nfriends who worked together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up until earlier, yes.\NBut that's no longer the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you guys really are traitors?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.91,0:10:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.88,0:10:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, I promised him
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that we'd beat the crap out of those\Nwho're trying to kill Ice pops together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you siding with Paulie?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.26,0:10:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I have some business\Nwith you people, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Robin! Why are you with jerks like them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.31,0:10:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna leave us, tell us the reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right! They said they work\Nfor the Government! So why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not listening, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did say goodbye to Cook and Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't tell them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:11:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did! But I can't accept it, either! Why, Robin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To make my wish come true...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A wish that can never come true if I'm with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to make it happen, I don't\Ncare what sacrifices need to be made!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why... you set your friends up\Nas assassins without hesitation?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that wish of yours?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.84,0:11:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.71,0:11:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That woman is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you out of your mind, Nico Robin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you realize what you're about to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You no longer have the right to say anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your mouth shut!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.31,0:11:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let anyone get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.67,0:12:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let anyone get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.47,0:12:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Robin! What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.73,0:12:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really mean it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.06,0:12:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin! What happened to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.99,0:12:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really our enemy now?! Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I need you guys to stop now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.54,0:13:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to find an important\Nperson now, so we're in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We no longer have business here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have any business\Nwith you guys, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kalifa, how much time is left?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.27,0:13:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know this is sudden, but this building\Nis to be set aflame in two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.24,0:13:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire is an effective tool for\Ndestroying various types of evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.74,0:13:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't wanna burn to death,\Nyou should leave the building immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.46,0:13:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that is, if you could.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they intend to eliminate us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It also seems that Nico Robin\Nwants to be on their side.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:14:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, were you able to accept\NRobin's leaving the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you don't have to shout like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon, several rooms on the first\Nfloor will burst into flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.79,0:14:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the culprits are pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things like this can happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastards...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.34,0:14:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that you do as you please\Nwhile pretending someone else did it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure have bad taste!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are already criminals. No harm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.31,0:14:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go on ahead and leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you completed your job. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't allow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.75,0:15:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...let Nico Robin go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where're you going this time...\Nwhen we finally found you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta my way, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Body.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.81,0:15:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are their bodies so hard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.19,0:15:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our bodies are well trained.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.15,0:15:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can raise our bodies' solidity\Nto be as hard as iron crust.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However... that's not to say\Ndefense is all we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.08,0:15:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paper Art.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.68,0:15:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh... He's dodging all the\Npunches... when he's that big!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:16:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's fluttering like paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.27,0:16:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You son of a...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.53,0:16:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--...Pistol!\N--Shave!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He disappeared, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your legs are so tremendously strong\Nthat it appears as if you disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You bastard!\N--Moon Walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.84,0:16:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you can even kick the air and float.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's flying! What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And... Tempest Kick.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.11,0:16:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A slashing attack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.07,0:16:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.63,0:17:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they just cut the wall by kicking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.21,0:17:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's possible if you can kick fast\Nenough to cause a gust of sharp wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We call it Tempest Kick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We met on your ship, didn't we, Roronoa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't a shipwright, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, could that assessment\Nof our ship you made be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.75,0:17:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately... I made the\Nassessment of the ship seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.38,0:17:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's indeed unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.89,0:18:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.73,0:18:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not done talking yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.28,0:18:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we are. I'll never see you guys again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Hurry up and catch Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.64,0:18:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roronoa! You're quite confident,\Naren't you, taking your eyes off of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.57,0:18:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finger Pistol.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need bullets to\Nshoot through human bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...bastard...! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy got caught so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.60,0:19:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Nico Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.25,0:19:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can they be that strong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.83,0:20:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've lived in a different environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.37,0:20:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since we, CP9 members, can remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.12,0:20:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we've been prepared to risk\Nour lives for the Government
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and trained to surpass the\Nlimits of human abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a result,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.51,0:20:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we've mastered the superhuman\Ntechniques called the Six Powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you've fully learned by now
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.19,0:20:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that the four of us, who have been entrusted\Nwith the World Government's vital tasks,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.19,0:21:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are in a whole different league\Nfrom you guys, a mere pirate group.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.25,0:21:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a world-class top secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.25,0:21:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a matter that people\Nlike you can get involved in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.59,0:21:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucci...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.47,0:21:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time for the igniters\Nto go off. We have to hurry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.06,0:21:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is a rare occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.39,0:21:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me show you something\Ninteresting before we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?\N--Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.12,0:21:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucci... What the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.08,0:21:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.69,0:22:23.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A piece of a dream that we started grasping
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.11,0:22:26.65,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Chasing after something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.65,0:22:32.24,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We send our aspirations sailing into the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.24,0:22:34.54,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when we're exhausted
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.54,0:22:37.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a compass that can\Nsearch for something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.71,0:22:43.13,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you think we can keep it forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.13,0:22:46.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,At the end of the dream\Nthat we will reach someday
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.05,0:22:49.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to be adults as we\Nare now as much as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.09,0:22:51.80,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We pray to this endless sky that we look up at
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.80,0:22:54.89,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.89,0:22:57.68,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wild fantasies from our childhood
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.68,0:23:00.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We trace unforgettable memories
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.52,0:23:06.19,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And try to keep the embers\Nburning that still consume us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.19,0:23:09.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To this familiar sunny sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.11,0:23:11.82,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Together we entrust our feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.82,0:23:14.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We go beyond the changing time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.41,0:23:19.12,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.09,0:23:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! He's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.46,0:23:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that appearance?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.96,0:23:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how I really look.\NWe're done with you guys now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.26,0:23:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat, can you defeat him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.30,0:23:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's huge, but I'll beat him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.97,0:23:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph! I'll let you experience\Nmy strongest power!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.73,0:23:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.81,0:23:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Straw Hat Pirates Annihilated?\NThe Menace of the Leopard Model!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.07,0:23:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
